y degree."],[2686,2861,"As long"],[2861,2986,"as my security's by your side."],[3048,3123,"What?"],[3123,3307,"Security at school?"],[3311,3432,"I'm already going to be pregnant."],[3432,3553,"I don't need more attention"],[3553,3749,"being drawn to me from a bodyguard."],[3828,3928,"Then I'll go undercover"],[3928,4012,"with you."],[4300,4458,"You wouldn't."],[4458,4642,"You don't make the rules here."],[4717,4792,"So if you really want"],[4792,4971,"that degree so badly,"],[5000,5117,"then I'm coming with you."]],"19":[[1209,1388,"Yes, Don Lavigne."],[2085,2135,"I don't mind"],[2135,2314,"staying in a dorm, you know."],[2314,2456,"Well, does a dorm room"],[2456,2686,"have heated floors, a sauna,"],[2756,2898,"a masseuse at your call?"],[2898,3057,"Point taken."],[3057,3178,"Well,"],[3178,3332,"that should be all of it."],[3332,3499,"And if you need anything,"],[3499,3678,"let Antoine know."],[3757,3937,"Oh, and"],[3970,4112,"And?"],[4112,4262,"If word got out that you're"],[4262,4441,"not from a mafia family yourself,"],[4508,4617,"the rest of the family wouldn't"],[4617,4796,"accept our heir as legitimate."],[4971,5088,"It is vital"],[5088,5267,"that you keep your pregnancy a secret."],[5313,5455,"Especially from Anita."],[5455,5618,"I can try. Who's Anita?"],[5618,5847,"No. You must, okay?"],[5851,6031,"And"],[6056,6222,"she's my head of housekeeping."],[6222,6402,"She has a soft spot for my ex Lydia,"],[6460,6610,"the Costello family's daughter."],[6610,6819,"And she wants me to take her back"],[6819,6998,"after she cheated on me."],[7011,7269,"Obviously, that's not going to happen."],[7503,7624,"Great."],[7624,7699,"Here she comes."]],"20":[[325,504,"I need a mafia 101."],[529,671,"Anita."],[671,850,"Good day."],[875,1059,"Sir."],[1230,1451,"I see you have a guest."],[1572,1751,"Will she be staying long?"],[1785,1914,"Anita,"],[1914,2093,"this is my fiancée, Vanessa."],[2156,2335,"Please make sure she's comfortable."],[2356,2535,"Fiancée?"],[2602,2781,"But you've never brought her around."],[2848,3028,"Are you questioning me?"],[3028,3207,"No, signore."],[3415,3465,"Hi."],[3465,3603,"I'm Vanessa Peters."],[3603,3782,"Peters?"],[3987,4124,"I've never heard of a Peters"],[4124,4304,"family in the mafia."],[4329,4425,"It's..."],[4425,4604,"It's not."],[4604,4738,"Then why would the boss"],[4738,5000,"bring a non mafia like you home?"],[5255,5463,"What's going on here?"]],"21":[[145,346,"Peters, it's a fake name."],[379,508,"I had to change my identity."],[508,709,"My family is under investigation."],[738,938,"And which family would that be?"],[955,1071,"I can't tell you that."],[1071,1167,"I'll just be going now."],[1167,1363,"I can take my own things."],[1363,1572,"A true mafia heiress"],[1580,1680,"would never dream"],[1680,1881,"of picking up her own bags."],[1885,2085,"Right. I knew that."],[2089,2218,"Which is why you should hurry up"],[2218,2318,"and get someone else to do it."],[2318,2489,"So I don't have to."],[2489,2748,"I know a lying skank when I see one."],[2781,2944,"She must have fooled Don Lavigne"],[2944,3007,"somehow."],[3044,3290,"And now she's after the family's fortune."],[3336,3574,"I'll expose this gold digging whore"],[3574,3774,"if it's the last thing I do."],[3795,4012,"Not so fast, Miss Peters."],[4546,4696,"Antoine has informed me"],[4696,4875,"that you will be accompanying"],[4875,4942,"Don Lavigne"],[4942,5142,"to each of the major houses."],[5188,5347,"Then you will need to be briefed"],[5347,5580,"on each of the most powerful Dons."],[5634,5764,"So"],[5764,5930,"Don Lavigne is running for"],[5930,6072,"mafia president?"],[6139,6314,"I'm sure you could explain it to me."],[6314,6448,"Please."],[6448,6694,"He's too busy to babysit you."],[6877,7052,"This will be a perfect opportunity"],[7052,7253,"for me to test..."],[7332,7494,"refresh your table etiquette"],[7494,7657,"as an heiress."],[7657,7874,"Crap. Where's Marcello?"],[7874,8074,"I'm going to give everything away."],[8095,8279,"After you,